cc:Work.dc:title: Artic North Pole Scene and Action View
cc:Work.dc:description: This a scene full of action in the cartoon artic.It includes the coloring of drawings (tree, santa, reindeer, panda skaters) from one of the coloring books included in the coloring book competition. Some figures were also added ...taken from Open Clipart's graphic base. There it is a combination of coloring, placement, alteration and remix.
